Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.69,0:23:05.95,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\3c&H000000&\3a&H80&\bord1\blur5}内心为何如此欣喜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.95,0:23:09.08,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\3c&H000000&\3a&H80&\bord1\blur5}可又为何如此悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.08,0:23:12.29,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\3c&H000000&\3a&H80&\bord1\blur5}此刻 我依然在你身边眺望
